Your AI partner on desktop. Fast, focused, and designed for deep work. Talk to Claude, anywhere you go.

Claude is a desktop application that helps you focus on your work. It's designed to be fast, focused, and to help you get more done.

Claude is built on top of the latest AI models from Anthropic, including access to Anthropic's newest and smartest model.

Do more on your PC with Claude:

- Instant answers—Use the [Control + Alt + Space] keyboard shortcut for faster access to Claude
- Stay productive—Keep Claude easily accessible next to your open apps with the companion window
- Upload files and photos—Summarize and analyze multiple documents

